WEBVTT

8afe9de4-4ca2-409b-89f1-0c0e0dda622d-0
00:00:00.480 --> 00:00:03.085
Most e-mail programs let you
create and save the contact

8afe9de4-4ca2-409b-89f1-0c0e0dda622d-1
00:00:03.085 --> 00:00:05.280
information of the people you
communicate with.

b8ab17ec-92d3-4bd2-8c2b-779e7971e57a-0
00:00:05.880 --> 00:00:08.467
This makes it easy to not only
send emails to them without

b8ab17ec-92d3-4bd2-8c2b-779e7971e57a-1
00:00:08.467 --> 00:00:10.836
having to look U their
information each time, but you

b8ab17ec-92d3-4bd2-8c2b-779e7971e57a-2
00:00:10.836 --> 00:00:13.511
can also save other imortant
information about your contacts

b8ab17ec-92d3-4bd2-8c2b-779e7971e57a-3
00:00:13.511 --> 00:00:15.880
that can easily be looked U or
referenced at anytime.

fac97789-247e-48a0-8b7a-d851e7a66539-0
00:00:16.840 --> 00:00:19.919
A contact can be as basic as a
name and e-mail address or

fac97789-247e-48a0-8b7a-d851e7a66539-1
00:00:19.919 --> 00:00:22.944
include information like a
street address, multile phone

fac97789-247e-48a0-8b7a-d851e7a66539-2
00:00:22.944 --> 00:00:25.439
numbers, a photo, or any other
relevant notes.

1f720718-64b0-49a6-b0b1-5734b13119a5-0
00:00:26.360 --> 00:00:28.968
Here in Microsoft Outlook you
can add contacts in a couple of

1f720718-64b0-49a6-b0b1-5734b13119a5-1
00:00:28.968 --> 00:00:29.600
different ways.

926b455d-ca8d-402c-b5fe-55292c1350f8-0
00:00:30.440 --> 00:00:33.101
If you received an e-mail
message from someone and you

926b455d-ca8d-402c-b5fe-55292c1350f8-1
00:00:33.101 --> 00:00:35.811
want to add them to your
contacts, right click on their

926b455d-ca8d-402c-b5fe-55292c1350f8-2
00:00:35.811 --> 00:00:38.280
e-mail address and choose Add to
Outlook Contacts.

cb5890ad-471a-4aff-b546-849a65ed0515-0
00:00:39.160 --> 00:00:42.025
In the window that opens, you'll
see any details that Outlook was

cb5890ad-471a-4aff-b546-849a65ed0515-1
00:00:42.025 --> 00:00:44.586
able to pull from the e-mail
already filled in here, so we

cb5890ad-471a-4aff-b546-849a65ed0515-2
00:00:44.586 --> 00:00:46.280
have the full name and e-mail
address.

c51dc66d-ebf2-4043-b908-98792c436f86-0
00:00:47.200 --> 00:00:50.390
If you have any other info, you
can fill in other fields, like

c51dc66d-ebf2-4043-b908-98792c436f86-1
00:00:50.390 --> 00:00:53.378
the company this person works
for, their title, a web page

c51dc66d-ebf2-4043-b908-98792c436f86-2
00:00:53.378 --> 00:00:56.366
associated with them, hone
numbers and if you have a photo

c51dc66d-ebf2-4043-b908-98792c436f86-3
00:00:56.366 --> 00:00:58.999
of them, you can add it by
clicking this icon here.

fe731b53-2be3-455f-b330-38ff694b3d3b-0
00:00:59.460 --> 00:01:02.411
You can also use this notes area
for any other info you may want

fe731b53-2be3-455f-b330-38ff694b3d3b-1
00:01:02.411 --> 00:01:05.182
to remember, for example their
birthday or the name of their

fe731b53-2be3-455f-b330-38ff694b3d3b-2
00:01:05.182 --> 00:01:05.500
spouse.

20e322bd-ebdf-418f-807d-b74d8dbd11e2-0
00:01:06.300 --> 00:01:09.603
When you're done, click Save and
close and the next time you want

20e322bd-ebdf-418f-807d-b74d8dbd11e2-1
00:01:09.603 --> 00:01:12.505
to send an e-mail to this
contact, just click New e-mail,

20e322bd-ebdf-418f-807d-b74d8dbd11e2-2
00:01:12.505 --> 00:01:15.408
start typing their name and
you'll be able to select them

20e322bd-ebdf-418f-807d-b74d8dbd11e2-3
00:01:15.408 --> 00:01:16.659
from Outlook suggestions.

c0fa8744-3688-4924-85c2-36808c2bb04b-0
00:01:16.660 --> 00:01:18.540
I'll just close this for now.

8b749a2f-8053-4a3e-8da8-41c23f8dceaa-0
00:01:20.340 --> 00:01:22.140
Now you can also add contacts
from scratch.

8aec6aa7-57e3-4c7e-9740-744d40f7ca88-0
00:01:22.460 --> 00:01:25.230
For example, if someone gives
you their business card and you

8aec6aa7-57e3-4c7e-9740-744d40f7ca88-1
00:01:25.230 --> 00:01:27.866
want to file their contact info
in Outlook, just click the

8aec6aa7-57e3-4c7e-9740-744d40f7ca88-2
00:01:27.866 --> 00:01:30.681
People icon here at the bottom
of the window and this is where

8aec6aa7-57e3-4c7e-9740-744d40f7ca88-3
00:01:30.681 --> 00:01:32.290
you'll find your existing
contacts.

02d7f4cf-7a8c-4b7a-9dfe-ae057a12de46-0
00:01:33.210 --> 00:01:36.304
Click the New Contact button
here at the top and from here

02d7f4cf-7a8c-4b7a-9dfe-ae057a12de46-1
00:01:36.304 --> 00:01:37.930
enter any relevant information.

88b8b72a-acbe-47c2-8fd7-548490f08288-0
00:01:38.610 --> 00:01:45.090
Oi can type in Jess's name, her
job title, her e-mail address.

c98fa1f5-5d4c-4727-901d-76cedba7c8e5-0
00:01:46.690 --> 00:01:49.864
If I have a photo of her, I can
click the photo and there's her

c98fa1f5-5d4c-4727-901d-76cedba7c8e5-1
00:01:49.864 --> 00:01:52.890
headshot, so I'll select that
and I can even add some notes.

5876a737-7a48-452f-84f2-73b92a3d2dae-0
00:01:52.890 --> 00:01:56.631
And again, when I'm done, I can
click Save and close and the

5876a737-7a48-452f-84f2-73b92a3d2dae-1
00:01:56.631 --> 00:02:00.310
next time I need to send an
e-mail to Jess I can just click

5876a737-7a48-452f-84f2-73b92a3d2dae-2
00:02:00.310 --> 00:02:03.868
new e-mail, start typing her
name, there she is and the 2

5876a737-7a48-452f-84f2-73b92a3d2dae-3
00:02:03.868 --> 00:02:05.340
field is now filled out.

